        -:  706:// Logic for distributing data into bins (Optimized to O(N))
        -:  707:static void compute_hist_logic(NV *restrict x, size_t n, NV *restrict breaks, size_t n_bins, 
        -:  708: size_t *restrict counts, NV *restrict mids, NV *restrict density) {
